Class Boat

java.lang.Object
Boat
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Boat extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a boat with its characteristics, purchase details, and expenses. Implements Serializable to allow object serialization.
Author:
Muhammad Ahsan Saleem
